929
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:34,250
I'm taking your sister and brother-in-law
to pray for a child.

930
00:39:34,250 --> 00:39:36,080
They say Goddess Mountain
is very effective.

931
00:39:36,080 --> 00:39:36,730
Mother.

932
00:39:37,290 --> 00:39:38,250
Go, Sister.

933
00:39:38,250 --> 00:39:39,290
I want to go too.

934
00:39:39,290 --> 00:39:41,350
You know I love going to temple fairs.

935
00:39:41,480 --> 00:39:41,940
Mother.

936
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,920
Let's take Susu with us then.

937
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:45,330
Let's go.

938
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:46,510
Uncle Feng Er.

939
00:39:46,510 --> 00:39:46,840
Here.

