964
00:40:21,810 --> 00:40:23,600
Happy New Year.

965
00:40:24,560 --> 00:40:25,960
Everyone is here.

966
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,560
I'm happy

967
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:30,330
you came to wish me a Happy New Year.

968
00:40:30,330 --> 00:40:32,730
But I can't accept these.

969
00:40:33,560 --> 00:40:36,340
We sent food to every household
before New Year.

970
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:37,360
That's been our Fei family tradition

971
