985
00:41:07,960 --> 00:41:10,000
I'll wish you all a Happy New Year too.

986
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:12,060
May you harvest more grain next year.

987
00:41:12,250 --> 00:41:13,160
Thank you, Madam!

988
00:41:13,160 --> 00:41:15,120
