1003
00:41:50,370 --> 00:41:51,530
You love to talk and laugh.

1004
00:41:51,530 --> 00:41:51,970
Yes.

1005
00:41:57,330 --> 00:41:57,850
Sister.

1006
00:41:58,290 --> 00:41:59,810
